{"tid":781880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵：高鐵地底主體工程難百分百防水","createTime":"2018-08-16T09:12:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T11:38:10.000Z","uid":37554,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"afdbcff7ee6c452569dcc729d46102e4bf6f9a83","tid":781880,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T09:12:00.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】高鐵香港段被指多處嚴重漏水，港鐵稱高鐵主體工程主要在地底，很難百分百防水，滲水情況並不罕見，但現時隧道和車站大致乾爽，水印亦是標準下可容許，之前曾經灌漿補救，但無透露到多少處要灌漿。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵又指，將於九月一及二日舉辦高鐵車站開放日讓市民參觀，港鐵將於今月25日免費派發門票，每人最多可取得四張同時段門票。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵總經理(高速鐵路)鄧維勇：「我們在這半年至一年有很多巡查，分別由政府部門、各部門以及政府的顧問也巡查我們的隧道，以及西九龍總站。當然我們現有的情況是大致乾爽，亦說了有些濕或者輕微滲水，水印的地方這是標準可容許，如果我們看見有滴水情況，會立即做適當措施作灌漿工作。」"},{"pid":"b9e343f08dd602feb76c8a421607af9ad0144412","tid":781880,"uid":42188,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T09:13:56.000Z","msg":"支那話地底屬於支那領土<br />\n咁港鐵算唔算洩露國家機密？"},{"pid":"0239ae09e74ca9515582d4ba3f9aa2a5eee09a23","tid":781880,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T09:14:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2018/08/Mass%20Transit%20Railway-%E9%AB%98%E9%90%B5-20180816153614_1f26_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2018%2F08%2FMass%2520Transit%2520Railway-%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2590%25B5-20180816153614_1f26_large.jpg&h=7b9837c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/jeremytammanho/videos/246627519521870/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjeremytammanho%2Fvideos%2F246627519521870%2F&d=hmXJPBa3pcuiSTTUdUP3QNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=47b7d117\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/jeremytammanho/videos/246627519521870/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0db1dadff31f620f447ecb76e4a3347ee25788","tid":781880,"uid":8048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"ci